    "how_to_grow": {
        "cultivation": "May be grown outdoors in frost-free areas, in well drained soil with protection from strong sunlight and excess wet. Indoors, grow in a mix of equal parts loam, leaf mould, peat substitute and sharp sand, in bright, filtered light with moderate humidity. Water moderately when in growth (avoiding the crown) but reduce humidity and water as the leaves fade. Keep completely dry when dormant",
